text: Yury Zyabrev (2 April 1947 - 11 November 2006) was a Soviet equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:2006 deaths Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
